Class manifestParserTests

  • java.lang.Object
    • tests.manifestParserTests

  • public class manifestParserTests
extends java.lang.Object
    Version:
    1.0 Please note: When running CSV tests, make sure you are overwriting the CSV each time. Otherwise, when you finish the first parsing test and try to do the second, the first will fail This is on purpose to make sure you are overwriting and not appending.
    Author:
    Locke
